Enum MovieAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MovieAttribute>
      • me.tobiadeyinka.itunessearch.entities.MovieAttribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<MovieAttribute>

    public enum MovieAttribute
extends java.lang.Enum<MovieAttribute>
    Enumeration of movie attributes that can be used to narrow down searches. See attribute parameter key in Searching the iTunes Store for more details. Created by Tobi Adeyinka on 2017. 10. 16..
